*.jar
*.war
*.nar
*.ear
*.zip
*.tar.gz
*.rar

# Sensitive config (never commit real API keys)
# Keep application.properties in version control but make sure
# ai.api.key= is left blank — use the GROQ_API_KEY env variable instead